strings: <voice_0x010009D5><se_low>*: You must meet your friend! WAITING TIME!
<voice_0x010009D6><se_low>*: to understand! This is just my set of tools.
<voice_0x010009D7><se_low>*: Nature I give you the promised reward...
<voice_0x010009DA><se_low>*: Without a doubt, this is your mascot...
<Cap><hero> There are 8 cheeses in a package.
<voice_0x010009DC><se_low>*: It might be hard cheese but rats like it.
<voice_0x010009DD><se_low>*: I could be wrong, but try it next time you encounter a monster...
<voice_0x010009DE><se_low>*: I don't know what will happen!
<voice_0x010009DF><se_low>*: But I'm tired of this useless life. Thanks again for returning the package.
